reviews.text: Price for each dish is expensive, the noodle bowl is very big but ingredients inside cannot give you a full feeling. Real dish looks quite different than the photo in menu
Lunch set is good. The non traditional papaya salad and the scallop pasta were unexpectedly yum

Nice fusion Thai food and why I place a five star on this Resturant is because I think the service and food are slightly different than other franchise shop ....  So when you past by to whampoa maybe give it a try ....

除了椰子蛋糕，我找不到任何賣點。職員更先安排客人坐當風位，直至客人要求調換位置。我戲言這間餐廳提供的菜式很有cafe特色：份量很少，$400也未必夠2人分享。但我忘記了這間餐廳正是叫「cafe」🤬
